  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK307">
<l>ciṉattaip poruḷeṉṟu koṇṭavaṉ kēṭu</l>
<l>nilatteṟintāṉ kaipiḻaiyā taṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Destruction will come upon him who regards anger as a good thing, as surely as the hand of him who strikes the ground will not fail.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
